Ethics & Compliance Hotline – Employees, Contractors, Agents & Suppliers
As part of Pacific Drilling’s commitment to our values of integrity and accountability, we provide an Ethics and Compliance Hotline for reporting incidents of illegal, unethical or other wrongful behavior. Anonymity will be maintained for those who do not disclose their identities.
To submit a report:

*Call +1 (800) 520-7724;
*Visit company's Ethics & Compliance 
website  here; or
*Email pdcompliance@pacificdrilling.com




