Join Our Talent Community





As a thriving drilling contractor, we seek and hire dedicated, passionate people who want to grow with us. Imagine a company primed with potential, a challenging and supportive environment, and the most advanced ultra-deepwater drillships. If that vision is inspiring, Pacific Drilling may be the place for you.




Offshore Careers





Our offshore employees work on a modern, high-specification fleet of ultra-deepwater drillships. From our safety equipment to our crew accommodations, we provide a best-in-class experience. This provides the capability for best-in-class performance from our employees.


Learn More
 View Current Career Opportunities




Office Careers





Our office employees play a significant role in supporting our operations. We strive to hire those who are the best at what they do. We value people’s strengths and challenge them to make a difference within our organization.


Learn More
 View Current Career Opportunities




Why Pacific Drilling





Our employees are consistently excited by the opportunity to directly impact the success of our growing company. They’re thrilled to work in an environment where everyone is recognized as an individual and given the tools and resources to be their best. And, we all have a shared passion for success that elevates the standard of everything we do, foremost our commitment to safe operations.


Learn More










