Fraud Alert: Pacific Drilling is aware that unauthorized individuals have recently promised employment allegedly on our behalf. These employment offers were supported by fake documents and included payment requests for fees and other transactions.
Pacific Drilling does not charge any application, processing or training fees as part of the recruitment process. Pacific Drilling only accepts applications for employment through our website, and we do not use job placement agencies to process hiring of candidates on our behalf.


